thread.title: Cu Leone Blends
thread.title_full: Culinary Depot reviewed by Cu Leone Blends

author: Cu Leone Blends
title: Cu Leone Blends
text: Culinary Depot provided exceptional service when we purchased our buffalo bowl chopper. Their pricing and payment plan were fair and reasonable. Shipping was superb. I cannot say the same about the Univex bowl chopper nor grinding attachment I have since purchased for the bowl chopper. Univex customer service and tech department have been very unresponsive to the problems we have had with the equipment since purchase.
